    "Application of Lemma 1 shows that P † (λ) is smooth with parameter L D. Therefore, by the duality between smoothness and strong convexity [19], P ⋆ (λ) is strongly concave with parameter 1/L D over E. B.7 Proof of Lemma 5Proof.",
    "First, we show that λ ⋆ p is a supergradient of the perturbation function P ⋆ (ϵ), i.e., λ ⋆ p ∈ ∂P ⋆ (ϵ ⋆ (λ ⋆ p)).",
